On registration you will have 2 pieces of
information which must be submitted as part of your requests.

With just basic vehicle identification by VIN or YMM, the only fields that
will be valid are:

  * Decode
  * Port
  * TSB
  * Maintenance List
  * Recall
  * Warranty

To get Vehicle History Report a VIN must be provided.

For data on repair or diagnostics, submission of the mileage and dtcs are
needed in addition to the vehicle information.
To check the maintenance and upcoming fields, mileage information is required.
